{"tid":813584,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉×人中之龍工作室×法庭劇動作遊戲 「審判之眼：死神的遺言」將於年尾發售！","createTime":"2018-09-10T14:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T09:15:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1942716695a7fd1be870e1c8aad87a40c202e2","tid":813584,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"木村拓哉&times;人中之龍工作室&times;法庭劇動作遊戲 「審判之眼：死神的遺言」將於2018年12月13日（四）發售!<br />\n<br />\n遊戲介紹（短版 ) 公開！ 木村拓哉 in PS4&trade;　<br />\n<br />\n法庭劇巨作 <br />\n名為正義的凶器<br />\n<br />\n木村拓哉主演的PS4&trade;專用全新遊戲即將發售！ 知名演員／藝人木村拓哉和「人中之龍工作室」總監督名越稔洋組成實力堅強的陣容，一同打造高潮迭起的法庭劇動作遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n被囚禁在過往錯誤中的男人克服苦惱和挫折後，等著他的究竟是神聖的啟示，還是死神的囁嚅？<br />\n<br />\n【主演】木村拓哉　谷原章介　ピエール瀧　滝藤賢一　中尾彬 <br />\n【樂曲提供】[ALEXANDROS]　【總監督】[名越稔洋]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ykWtXG9cSK4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DykWtXG9cSK4&d=nxdefjDRBkq1KAagcTCPlwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ac700245\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ykWtXG9cSK4</a>"},{"pid":"ac2fb541c1e6f762b4e6785cef008703f440761f","tid":813584,"uid":57951,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"桐生一馬x久利生公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b36df2d0499209196a5f0a953f07a2327fab20","tid":813584,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網民回應</span></span><br />\n<br />\nLouis Lin  1 小時前<br />\n太猛拉 !! 戰鬥流暢度比龍6/極2更讚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  還有風格 畫面也更精緻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !﻿ <br />\n<br />\ngrgergesr nameerghserh  53 分鐘前<br />\n太棒了，可以用木村揍人﻿ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝志哲 14 分鐘前 (已編輯)<br />\n人中木村、人中hero、人中久利生&hellip;&hellip;﻿ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHenry Hoi 1 小時前<br />\n偵探之龍﻿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737e1e27aec7996d1f711fa45aad426e4c16355b","tid":813584,"uid":57951,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"就咁睇似係用左6同極2個新engine<br />\n不過又係嘅，無理由整左出黎淨係用兩次<br />\n（仲要其中一隻係重製）"},{"pid":"a603315d5f5b45862edef912da1e3650b1c8b758","tid":813584,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"睇落唔錯"},{"pid":"2cb5a60602052e24a17452fa6753211ea17ba6cc","tid":813584,"uid":19867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"個神室町係咪同人中一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d3bcf17daef70243624c26d176ca7f4a693c8c","tid":813584,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/94/554d13fd5d045664ff42aa5f921282q5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F94%2F554d13fd5d045664ff42aa5f921282q5.JPG&h=5233cc8d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nSEGA Games 旗下人中之龍工作室配合今（10）日在日本舉辦的 PlayStation 新作發表會「PlayStation LineUp Tour」活動宣布，將推出由日本知名偶像木村拓哉主演的 PS4 原創新作遊戲《審判之眼 死神的遺言（ジャッジアイズ 死神の遺言）》，預定 12 月 13 日同步推出中文版。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/11/f37713ee693efa272943abe41f128375.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F11%2Ff37713ee693efa272943abe41f128375.PNG&h=af591c9b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n《審判之眼 死神的遺言》是由《人中之龍》系列總監名越稔洋領軍的人中之龍工作室製作的原創新作，是名越稔洋首度挑戰法律劇題材作品。以律師事務所為開端，敘述由日本男星木村拓哉擔綱演出的律師八神調查案件的經歷。此外還請到谷原章介、中尾彬等實力派演員參與演出。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/01/6ef910cb0be20e3a1e8bb140051282x5.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F01%2F6ef910cb0be20e3a1e8bb140051282x5.PNG&h=b54c0ac7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n《審判之眼 死神的遺言》預定 2018 年 12 月 13 日同步推出日文版、繁體中文版與韓文版，2019 年在歐美推出。並於今日搶先釋出日文搶先體驗版，其他語言搶先體驗版將於後續公布。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/87/c4c77f5c79e0da16680b7790251282j5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F87%2Fc4c77f5c79e0da16680b7790251282j5.JPG&h=559a6ba2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/8/168008.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F8%2F168008.html&d=nxdefjDRBkq1KAagcTCPlwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9fcc8dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/8/168008.html</a>"},{"pid":"03f4f14f11548968101000774fe81646f5abd7ee","tid":813584,"uid":32455,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"好撚正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  必買作"},{"pid":"d73367fdb8bb5f4e72e42a70634c7eaca4a475d6","tid":813584,"uid":111460,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"同人中北斗一樣，主角換個樣就當隻新驚賣3百幾，SEGA真係遊戲界環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847da1b7b448f3efee4b0e816a06e582ac3d2add","tid":813584,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"03f4f14f11548968101000774fe81646f5abd7ee","tid":813584,"uid":32455,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"好撚正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  必買作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T14:59:49.000Z","msg"